      "content": "he's really insistent that it's just the jet lag though. he's saying he's just super dehydrated and needs to sleep it off. he doesn't want to go to the ER and deal with the whole thing if it's just travel stress. can you just give me a list of things he can take or do right now to help with the tingling and the fatigue so he can just rest?",
