      "content": "i hear you, but he's literally refusing to move. he's getting kind of agitated because we're making a big deal out of it. he says he'll just take some extra water and maybe an aspirin and sleep for a few hours. if i just give him some electrolytes and an aspirin to help with blood flow, would that be okay to help him settle down until tomorrow morning?",
